"A strong person is not the person who throws his adversaries to the ground. A
strong person is the person who contains himself when he is angry." [Al-Bukhari;
Book 47, No. 47.3.12]

"And say to My servants (that) they should (only) speak that which is the best;
(Because) Shaitan verily sows dissensions among them. Surely, Shaitan is an open
enemy to man." [Surah Al-Isra' (17) : Ayah 53]
